title: Sakura Letter Bag
description:
Mots Doux à ma Chérie is our collection for true romantics and lovers of vintage aesthetics. 

Whether you are going on a Valentine’s Day date, having a cherry blossom picnic or simply feeling all lovey-dovey and cute, our Mots Doux à ma Chérie letter bag is the perfect accessory for the occasion. 

The bag is made from vegan leather and is shaped like a big envelope complete with a scalloped edge, sakura seal and sakura stamp on the back. 

It has a huge pink bow on top that doubles as a handle and can be worn either as a shoulder bag or as a backpack thanks to its interchangeable strap locations.

It is 35 x 26 x 10 cm (13.8 x 10.2 x 3.9 inch) in size, making it big enough to fit in A4 documents, and has lots of compartments – including two with a zipper and one water bottle sized – to safely carry everything you’ll need on a day out.

This item is made by Fluffy Tori in Switzerland. it ships from our US warehouse.
